CIMAC pixel clustering and cell clustering, include calibration channel for pixel clustering

Candace Liu

December 4, 2020

  • First do pixel clustering, then do cell clustering using frequency of pixel clusters
  • Gaussian blur sigma=2, k=20 (pixel metaclusters)
  • For each pixel, divide each marker by total (each pixel sums to 1)
  • z-score cap=3 for hierarchical clustering
  • k=10 (cell metaclusters)
  • Include calibration channel when doing pixel frequency normalization
